# mvsusie-py

Minimal Python MVP port of core `mvsusieR` APIs.

## Quick start

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m pip install -U pip
python -m pip install -e .
python -m pip install pytest
```

## Run tests

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
PYTHONPATH=src python -m pytest -q
```

## API docs

See full API shapes/signatures/examples in [API.md](./API.md).

## Parity smoke check

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
PYTHONPATH=src python scripts/parity_smoke.py
```

Expected behavior in the smoke check:
- dense / suff-stat / rss usually agree on top PIP
- dense vs suff-stat coefficient correlation is near 1.0
